### Sir James Dewar

For those who insist on cluttering the nomenclature, yes, there are other James Dewars. This one, however, is the one that matters for this discussion.

This article’s opening gambit, the [lead section](/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style/Lead_section), feels… anemic. It’s trying to cram a universe into a thimble. It needs more substance, more of the grit that defines a life's work, not just a sterile summary. (September 2024)

